# Tron

NB. Redis connection pool size must be >= than the max number of threads
specified in the Procfile.

# Init

    $ createdb "tron_development" --encoding=utf-8
    $ sequel --migrate-directory db/migrations \
      postgres://localhost/tron_development
    $ foreman run ruby db/seeds.rb

# Example Usage

NB. All requests should have their associated API key.

    curl http://localhost:6000/servers

    curl http://localhost:6000/regions

    curl http://localhost:6000/funpacks

    curl http://localhost:6000/servers \
        -d name=minebnb \
        -d region={REGION_ID} \
        -d funpack={FUNPACK_ID}

    curl http://localhost:6000/servers/{SERVER_ID}/session \
        -X POST
